Place pre-trained PhysSDB checkpoints here. Layout expected by app.py:

  runs/
    baseline_an/model_best.pt
    baseline_pl/model_best.pt
    physsdb_an/model_best.pt
    physsdb_pl/model_best.pt

Download options (in order of convenience):
  1. ./bin/download-weights.sh                    (pulls from GitHub Release)
  2. git lfs pull                                 (if you cloned with LFS)
  3. Train them yourself with the scripts in this repo (train_sdb.py / train_phys.py)
